  Don't apply -strict-aliasing.patch anymore since it's in the .98 release.

*lvm2-2.02.98 (18 Jan 2013)

  18 Jan 2013; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> +lvm2-2.02.98.ebuild:
